'''''Daar doer in die bosveld''''' (Icyongereza: ''Far Away in Bushveld'' ) niyo film yambere yakozwe [[Afurika y’Epfo|numuyobozi wumunya Afrika yepfo]] Jamie Uys<ref>Daar Doer in die Bosveld - Mimosa Film Group <nowiki>http://www.mimosafilms.co.za</nowiki> › Archive › daar-doer-in...</ref> . Yasohotse bwa mbere mu 1951. <ref name="imdb">[[imdbtitle:0270903|imdb]]</ref> Filime iri mu [[Ikinyafurikansi|rurimi rwa Afrikaans]], ururimi rwihariye rwa [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo<ref>Daar doer in die bosveld - Alchetron, the free social ... <nowiki>https://alchetron.com</nowiki> › Daar-doer-in-...</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Iyi filime ni urwenya ku muhinzi ufite isoni witwa Hans Botha usabwa gufata umwarimu ukiri muto witwa Martie du Toit<ref>What does daar doer in die bosveld mean? - Definitions.net <nowiki>https://www.definitions.net</nowiki> › definition</ref>. Hans ageze aho bisi ihagarara gufata Martie arumirwa rwose kubera ubwiza bwe kandi abasha kuvuga gusa interuro<ref>Daar doer in die bosveld (hyperleap.com)</ref>, "It looks like rain.." na It was an accident." Bombi bahura ningorane nyinshi munzira; ahanini bitewe n'imodoka ya kera ya Hans<ref>Daar Doer in die Bosveld – Cast & Crew on MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › cast</ref>. Igihe bombi bageze aho Martie yerekeza, Martie atose kandi yemeza ko Hans ari igicucu. Hans, ariko, akunda byimazeyo Martie<ref>Daar Doer in die Bosveld Movie - Filmoria <nowiki>https://www.filmoria.co.uk</nowiki> › movie-list › daar-doer-in-...</ref>. 

